<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Fitter Fathers | Be the Dad They Deserve</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;600;700&family=Barlow:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
:root{
  --black:#090c0a;
  --off-black:#0e1210;
  --card:#111712;
  --sage:#7d9e80;
  --sage-light:#a6c2a8;
  --sage-pale:#c8dbc9;
  --sage-dim:#4e6b51;
  --sage-bg:rgba(125,158,128,0.07);
  --white:#eef3ee;
  --muted:#6b7d6c;
  --border:rgba(125,158,128,0.18);
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:17px;line-height:1.65;overflow-x:hidden;}

/* NAV */
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:100;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:20px 5vw;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(9,12,10,.97) 0%,transparent 100%);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);}
.nav-logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:.12em;color:var(--sage-light);text-decoration:none;}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:2rem;align-items:center;}
.nav-links a{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--white);text-decoration:none;opacity:.65;transition:opacity .2s,color .2s;}
.nav-links a:hover{opacity:1;color:var(--sage-light);}
.nav-cta{background:var(--sage)!important;color:var(--black)!important;padding:10px 22px;opacity:1!important;font-weight:700!important;transition:background .2s!important;}
.nav-cta:hover{background:var(--sage-light)!important;}

/* HERO */
.hero{position:relative;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;overflow:hidden;}
.hero-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background-size:cover;background-position:center 25%;}
.hero-bg::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,rgba(9,12,10,.3) 0%,rgba(9,12,10,.1) 35%,rgba(9,12,10,.75) 70%,var(--black) 100%);}
.hero-content{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:5rem 5vw 5rem;max-width:780px;}
.eyebrow{display:inline-block;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage-light);margin-bottom:1rem;border-left:3px solid var(--sage);padding-left:.9rem;}
.hero h1{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(3.5rem,8vw,7rem);line-height:1;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.hero h1 span{color:var(--sage-light);}
.hero-sub{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:400;color:rgba(238,243,238,.8);max-width:520px;line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2.5rem;}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.btn-sage{background:var(--sage);color:var(--black);padding:.85rem 2rem;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;transition:background .2s,transform .15s;}
.btn-sage:hover{background:var(--sage-light);transform:translateY(-2px);}
.btn-outline{border:1px solid var(--sage);color:var(--sage-pale);padding:.85rem 2rem;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:600;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;transition:all .2s;}
.btn-outline:hover{background:var(--sage-bg);color:var(--white);}

/* STATS */
.stats-bar{background:var(--sage);display:flex;justify-content:space-around;flex-wrap:wrap;}
.stat{flex:1;min-width:130px;padding:1.6rem 1rem;text-align:center;border-right:1px solid rgba(9,12,10,.15);}
.stat:last-child{border-right:none;}
.stat-num{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.4rem;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--black);line-height:1;}
.stat-label{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(9,12,10,.7);margin-top:.25rem;}

/* SECTIONS */
section{padding:6rem 5vw;}
.section-eyebrow{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:.75rem;}
.section-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4.2rem);letter-spacing:.04em;line-height:1.0;margin-bottom:1.5rem;}
.section-title span{color:var(--sage-light);}
.rule{width:48px;height:3px;background:var(--sage);margin-bottom:2rem;}

/* PROBLEM */
.problem{background:var(--off-black);}
.problem-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:4rem;max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;align-items:start;}
.body-copy{font-size:1rem;color:rgba(238,243,238,.75);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.pain-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:1rem;margin-top:1rem;}
.pain-item{display:flex;gap:1rem;align-items:flex-start;padding:1.2rem;background:var(--sage-bg);border-left:3px solid var(--sage-dim);}
.pain-icon{color:var(--sage);font-size:1.2rem;margin-top:.1rem;flex-shrink:0;}
.pain-item h4{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.05rem;letter-spacing:.04em;margin-bottom:.2rem;}
.pain-item p{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;}

/* ABOUT — split with photo */
.about{background:var(--black);padding:0;}
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;min-height:600px;}
.about-photo-col{background-size:cover;background-position:center 20%;min-height:560px;background-repeat:no-repeat;background-color:#0e1210;}
.about-text-col{padding:5rem 4rem;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;background:var(--off-black);}
.pull-quote{font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;font-size:1.35rem;font-style:italic;line-height:1.55;color:var(--sage-pale);margin-bottom:2rem;padding-left:1.5rem;border-left:3px solid var(--sage);}
.sig{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.3rem;letter-spacing:.1em;color:var(--sage);margin-top:1rem;}

/* WORKOUT BANNER */
.workout-banner{position:relative;min-height:480px;display:flex;align-items:center;overflow:hidden;}
.workout-bg{position:absolute;inset:0;background-size:cover;background-position:center 20%;}
.workout-bg::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to right,rgba(9,12,10,.92) 0%,rgba(9,12,10,.7) 50%,rgba(9,12,10,.15) 100%);}
.workout-content{position:relative;z-index:2;padding:4rem 5vw;max-width:600px;}
.workout-content h2{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);letter-spacing:.04em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.workout-content h2 span{color:var(--sage-light);}

/* PROGRAM */
.program{background:var(--off-black);}
.program-intro{text-align:center;max-width:620px;margin:0 auto 3.5rem;}
.tiers{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:1.5rem;max-width:1050px;margin:0 auto;}
.tier{border:1px solid var(--border);padding:2.5rem 2rem;background:var(--card);position:relative;}
.tier.featured{border-color:var(--sage);}
.tier-badge{position:absolute;top:-1px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--sage);color:var(--black);font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.65rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:.3rem 1.2rem;}
.tier-level{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:.4rem;}
.tier-name{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2rem;letter-spacing:.06em;margin-bottom:.5rem;}
.tier-desc{font-size:.88rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1.5rem;line-height:1.65;}
.tier-features{list-style:none;margin-bottom:2rem;}
.tier-features li{padding:.5rem 0;font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(238,243,238,.8);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(125,158,128,.08);display:flex;gap:.6rem;line-height:1.5;}
.tier-features li::before{content:"→";color:var(--sage);flex-shrink:0;margin-top:.05rem;}
.tier .btn-sage,.tier .btn-outline{width:100%;text-align:center;display:block;}
.tier-note{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--muted);text-align:center;margin-top:.75rem;}

/* HOW */
.how{background:var(--black);}
.steps-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:2.5rem;max-width:1000px;margin:2.5rem auto 0;counter-reset:steps;}
.step{counter-increment:steps;padding-top:3rem;position:relative;}
.step::before{content:counter(steps,decimal-leading-zero);font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:4rem;color:rgba(125,158,128,.12);position:absolute;top:0;left:0;line-height:1;}
.step h4{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:.06em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.5rem;color:var(--sage-pale);}
.step p{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;}

/* STAKES */
.stakes{background:var(--sage);padding:5rem 5vw;text-align:center;}
.stakes .section-eyebrow{color:rgba(9,12,10,.6);}
.stakes h2{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem);letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--black);margin-bottom:1.2rem;}
.stakes p{font-size:1.05rem;color:rgba(9,12,10,.75);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;line-height:1.75;}
.btn-dark{background:var(--black);color:var(--sage-light);padding:.85rem 2rem;font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:1rem;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block;transition:background .2s;}
.btn-dark:hover{background:var(--off-black);}
.stakes-sub{font-size:.8rem;color:rgba(9,12,10,.55);margin-top:1rem;font-style:italic;}

/* FOOTER */
footer{background:var(--off-black);border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:3.5rem 5vw 2rem;}
.footer-inner{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr;gap:3rem;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem;}
.footer-brand .nav-logo{display:block;margin-bottom:.6rem;}
.footer-brand p{font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.65;}
.footer-col h4{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:1rem;}
.footer-col a{display:block;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:.5rem;transition:color .2s;}
.footer-col a:hover{color:var(--sage-light);}
.footer-bottom{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding-top:1.5rem;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;}
.footer-bottom span,.footer-bottom a{font-size:.75rem;color:rgba(107,125,108,.5);text-decoration:none;}
.footer-bottom a:hover{color:var(--muted);}

/* RESPONSIVE */
@media(max-width:768px){
  nav{padding:16px 1.5rem;}
  .nav-links{display:none;}
  .problem-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  .about-photo-col{min-height:320px;}
  .about-text-col{padding:3rem 1.5rem;}
  .footer-inner{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
  section{padding:4rem 1.5rem;}
}
@keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(28px);}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}}
.hero-content>*{animation:fadeUp .7s ease both;}
.hero-content>.eyebrow{animation-delay:.1s;}
.hero-content>h1{animation-delay:.25s;}
.hero-content>.hero-sub{animation-delay:.4s;}
.hero-content>.hero-btns{animation-delay:.52s;}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Fitter Fathers</a>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#about">About</a>
    <a href="#program">Coaching</a>
    <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fitterfathers" target="_blank">@fitterfathers</a>
    <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank" class="nav-cta">Start Today</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO: Father-son kiss photo -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-bg" id="heroBg" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="eyebrow">Built for dads who are ready to lead.</div>
    <h1>Become the Father<br/><span>Your Family</span><br/>Deserves.</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">You show up for your job. You show up for your kids. But somewhere along the way, you stopped showing up for yourself — and you feel it every single day. That ends now.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank" class="btn-sage">Start Today →</a>
      <a href="#program" class="btn-outline">See Coaching Levels ↓</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">20+</div><div class="stat-label">Years Sober</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">500+</div><div class="stat-label">Men Coached</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">2</div><div class="stat-label">Coaching Levels</div></div>
  <div class="stat"><div class="stat-num">0</div><div class="stat-label">Excuses Accepted</div></div>
</div>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="problem">
  <div class="problem-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="section-eyebrow">Sound Familiar?</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">You're Not Lazy.<br/>You're Just <span>Lost.</span></h2>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <p class="body-copy">You wake up tired. You skip the workout again. You tell yourself tomorrow will be different — but it never is. And the worst part? You know exactly what you're capable of. You just can't figure out how to get back there.</p>
      <p class="body-copy">That gap between who you are and who you know you can be — that's the villain. Not motivation. Not time. Not your schedule. It's the absence of a proven system and someone in your corner who won't let you off the hook.</p>
      <p class="body-copy">I've been in that place. Mine almost killed me. Now I coach men out of it every single day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pain-list">
      <div class="pain-item">
        <div class="pain-icon">→</div>
        <div><h4>You're exhausted before noon</h4><p>Poor sleep, no movement, and compounding stress. That's not your age — that's your system being broken.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-item">
        <div class="pain-icon">→</div>
        <div><h4>You've lost the version of yourself you respected</h4><p>You remember who you were. The gap between that man and the mirror keeps getting wider.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-item">
        <div class="pain-icon">→</div>
        <div><h4>Every program you've tried has failed you</h4><p>Because they weren't built for dads. Your life has real constraints. Your system needs to match them.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="pain-item">
        <div class="pain-icon">→</div>
        <div><h4>Your kids are watching</h4><p>They're learning what a man looks like from you, every single day. What are they seeing?</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ABOUT: Family vacation photo -->
<div class="about" id="about">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-photo-col" id="aboutPhoto" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
    <div class="about-text-col">
      <div class="section-eyebrow">About Michael</div>
      <h2 class="section-title">I Was That Dad.<br/><span>Not Anymore.</span></h2>
      <div class="rule"></div>
      <p class="pull-quote">"Bad habits almost killed me. Great habits have made me the man I am today."</p>
      <p class="body-copy">I know exactly where you are because I lived it. Deep in addiction, disconnected from myself, watching my life happen to me instead of living it. I hit bottom hard. And then I made a decision.</p>
      <p class="body-copy">I built a system that worked — not just for me, but for the hundreds of fathers I've coached since. Dads who now sprint after their kids instead of watching from the couch. Dads who wake up and feel like the men they promised to be.</p>
      <p class="body-copy">I started Fitter Fathers because that transformation isn't just possible for every dad — it's your responsibility. Your family deserves the best version of you. Let's go build him.</p>
      <div class="sig">— Michael</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- WORKOUT BANNER: B&W dumbbell photo -->
<div class="workout-banner">
  <div class="workout-bg" id="workoutBg" style="background-image:url('data:image/jpeg;base64,')"></div>
  <div class="workout-content">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">The Work Is Real</div>
    <h2>No Shortcuts.<br/><span>No Excuses.</span><br/>Just Results.</h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <p class="body-copy" style="color:rgba(238,243,238,.8);">The program is built to fit your life — not the other way around. No 2-hour gym sessions. No complicated meal plans. Just a clear system that compounds into the version of yourself you've been waiting to get back to.</p>
    <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank" class="btn-sage" style="margin-top:1rem;">Join the Program →</a>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PROGRAM -->
<section class="program" id="program">
  <div class="program-intro">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">The Coaching</div>
    <h2 class="section-title" style="text-align:center;">Pick Your <span>Level.</span></h2>
    <div class="rule" style="margin:0 auto 1.5rem;"></div>
    <p class="body-copy" style="text-align:center;">Both tracks are built for busy dads. Pick the level of support that fits your life right now.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="tiers">
    <div class="tier">
      <div class="tier-level">Level 01</div>
      <div class="tier-name">The Foundation</div>
      <p class="tier-desc">The complete system — training, recipes, and community. Built for the father who is done doing things halfway.</p>
      <ul class="tier-features">
        <li>4-6 week training programs</li>
        <li>Complete workout library</li>
        <li>Curated Recipes</li>
        <li>Monthly community calls</li>
        <li>Private Fitter Fathers community</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank" class="btn-outline">Get Started →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="tier featured">
      <div class="tier-badge">Most Popular</div>
      <div class="tier-level">Level 02</div>
      <div class="tier-name">All In</div>
      <p class="tier-desc">Custom training. Personalized nutrition. Direct access to Michael. Built for the father who wants zero guesswork and someone in his corner.</p>
      <ul class="tier-features">
        <li>Everything in Level 1</li>
        <li><strong>Custom 12-week training</strong> — written for your goals, your schedule</li>
        <li><strong>Personalized nutrition coaching</strong> — real food, real results</li>
        <li><strong>Weekly Check-ins</strong> — you work, we adjust</li>
        <li><strong>Direct Messaging Access</strong> — 24/7 messaging with Michael</li>
        <li><strong>Weekly live community calls</strong> — the fam shows up and holds each other accountable</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank" class="btn-sage">Go All In →</a>
      <div class="tier-note">Limited spots — serious inquiries only</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section class="how">
  <div style="max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;">
    <div class="section-eyebrow">The Process</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Three Steps to<br/><span>Becoming That Dad.</span></h2>
    <div class="rule"></div>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step">
        <h4>01 — Start Today</h4>
        <p>Stop waiting for the right moment. There isn't one. Make the call. Sign up. That decision alone changes who you are from this moment forward.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h4>02 — Follow the System</h4>
        <p>No guesswork, no wasted effort. Every rep, every meal, every decision is mapped out. Your only job is to execute. We'll handle the rest.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <h4>03 — Win the Morning</h4>
        <p>Energy. Strength. Confidence. It all comes back when you own the first hours of your day. Your family will notice. Your kids will feel it. That's the whole point.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STAKES -->
<div class="stakes">
  <div class="section-eyebrow">The Decision Is Yours</div>
  <h2>A Year From Now, Who Are You?</h2>
  <p>Stronger. Leaner. Locked in. The dad your kids brag about. The husband your partner fell for. The man you promised yourself you'd become — or exactly where you are right now. The only variable is what you do today.</p>
  <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank" class="btn-dark">I Choose Better. Start Today →</a>
  <div class="stakes-sub">Limited spots available this month. Don't be the reason you don't do this.</div>
</div>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer>
  <div class="footer-inner">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Fitter Fathers</a>
      <p>Coaching fathers through real transformation — one habit at a time.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Coaching</h4>
      <a href="#program">Level 1 — The Foundation</a>
      <a href="#program">Level 2 — All In</a>
      <a href="https://invite.everfit.io/X4OUR712YW" target="_blank">Join Today</a>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Connect</h4>
      <a href="#about">About Michael</a>
      <a href="https://www.instagram.com/fitterfathers" target="_blank">@fitterfathers</a>
      <a href="mailto:info@thefitterfathers.com">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <span>© 2026 Fitter Fathers. All rights reserved.</span>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:2rem;">
      <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
      <a href="#">Terms &amp; Conditions</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>


</body>
</html>
